{"tid":1508882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【召集荃灣西手足】每晚10pm快閃海濱公園鳩叫！","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T14:06:31.000Z","uid":193592,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ef4e5afab08f224f14cda21c8f7a84c91ce423","tid":1508882,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"星期日荃葵青大遊行見各位手足咁團結，團火燒到咁勁當然唔好比佢停！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左響應全港每晚鳩叫大行動，喺到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">召集各位荃西街坊每晚10pm 落海濱公園大空地（荃灣體育館隔離）散步快閃，大家盡情鳩叫半個鐘</span></strong></span>！！！喺荃灣區集氣！！<br />\n亦鼓勵各區手足都開post召集街坊每晚一齊鳩叫！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">實行和理非遍地開花鳩叫大行動！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n香港警察，知法犯法！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">各自散步，一齊鳩叫！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#BeWater<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykhYmiJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykhYmiJ.jpg&h=b994026d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31868749d4b009989a0a39a96552d664f68bbf1e","tid":1508882,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"25459a11e59e429e64aa0aa920ac9c35052cfc46","tid":1508882,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"88f864a1922fe22ee211d6fdb390a6edbe01cc61","tid":1508882,"uid":193592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"38c16bee37afc7824b10361298087878e3c26a93","tid":15088